author: rhuijben
msg: Rev the svn_client_blame api. This to provide all revision properties to the
receiver and to allow specifying that a change only applies to the working copy
version of a file. (This last part will be a separate commit which will allow
blaming working copy versions of files)
(struct rev): Store rev_props hash instead of individual values.
(file_rev_handler): Copy rev_props hash instead of values.
(svn_client_blame5): ... this and call receiver using the new
hashes. Always set local_change to FALSE.
